description: The Hidden Truth of WWII Vol. Two War Documentary hosted by Stephen Rashbrook, published by History Channel broadcasted as part of HC The Lost Evidence series in 2006 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/2/26/The-Hidden-Truth-of-WWII-Vol.-Two-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ The History Channel series The Lost Evidence recounts the moments of key battles in the European and Pacific theaters through the use of recently unearthed reconnaissance photos that were taken during the actual battle as well as in the days and weeks prior. Interviews with men on both sides of each battle offer a fresh look at the war. Links ------------------------------ Source: http://docuwiki.net/index.php?title=The_Hidden_Truth_of_WWII_Vol._Two
